; Regression test for issue #2985: account() function fails when
; collapse_posts creates a <Total> posting with no parent account,
; preventing get_account() from walking up to the journal master.
= expr (commodity == '$' and account =~ /^Assets:/)
    (Allocation:Cash)                  1.000
= expr (commodity == 'FOO' and account =~ /^Assets:/)
    (Allocation:Equities)              1.000

2022/01/01 * Test
    Assets:Checking                     $123
    Income:Payroll
2022/02/01 * Test
    Assets:Checking                     $123
    Income:Payroll
2022/03/01 * Test
    Assets:Brokerage                    10 FOO @ $8
    Assets:Checking
2022/04/01 * Test
    Assets:Checking                     $123
    Income:Payroll

test reg --no-pager --collapse --plot-total-format "%(account('Allocation:Cash').total)\n" -J --monthly ^Allocation:
$123
$246
$246
$246
end test
